BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:murphy-week3-start@mcnamara-family.local
DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260317T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260317T203500
SUMMARY:WEEK 3 - Position Changes Begin
DESCRIPTION:WEEK 3 PROGRESSION - Change position every few nights:\n\nNights 1-2: Sitting on bed (not lying down)\nNights 3-4: Chair next to bed\nNights 5-6: Chair in middle of room\nNights 7-8: Chair at doorway\nNights 9-10: Hallway (you listening, not visible)\n\nStay at each position 3-5 nights. If big protest: stay extra 2 nights
LOCATION:Home - Murphy's room
CATEGORIES:BEDTIME
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:murphy-week4-start@mcnamara-family.local
DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260324T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260324T203000
SUMMARY:WEEK 4 - Exit Before Sleep (THE BIG SHIFT)
DESCRIPTION:She learns to fall asleep WITHOUT you in room\n\n8:00-8:25: Routine (pajamas, outfit, book, gratitude, hug)\n8:25-8:30: Quiet time in doorway\n8:30: YOU EXIT (she is drowsy but not asleep)\n\n8:35: First check-in (5 min after you left)\n8:40: Second check-in if needed\n8:45: Usually asleep\n\nDays 4-7: Extend intervals to 8 min between checks
LOCATION:Home - Murphy's room
CATEGORIES:BEDTIME
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:murphy-week5-start@mcnamara-family.local
DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T203000
SUMMARY:WEEK 5 - Extend Check-In Intervals
DESCRIPTION:Continue extending check-in intervals:\n\n5 min to 8 min to 10 min to 15 min\n\nBy mid-week: She asleep before first check-in\nBy end of week: One check-in is enough\n\nProgress:\nMon-Tue: 5 and 8 min\nWed-Thu: 8 and 10 min\nFri-Sun: 10 and 15 min
LOCATION:Home - Murphy's room
CATEGORIES:BEDTIME
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:murphy-week6-start@mcnamara-family.local
DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260407T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260407T201500
SUMMARY:WEEK 6 - INDEPENDENT SLEEP
DESCRIPTION:FINAL PHASE - Bedtime routine only. She sleeps alone.\n\n8:00-8:05: Pajamas and teeth\n8:05-8:10: Pick outfit\n8:10-8:20: One book\n8:20-8:25: Gratitude list\n8:25-8:27: Hug and kiss\n8:28: YOU LEAVE - Lights off, door mostly closed\n\n8:30: Check-in if you hear noise\nBy 9:00: She is asleep independently\n\nSUCCESS - You get your evening back
LOCATION:Home - Murphy's room
CATEGORIES:BEDTIME
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
