DESCRIPTION:Plan 5-6 dinners for the week\n- List ingredients\n- Note prep that can happen Sunday\n- Post on fridge\n\nSunday Prep (30 min):\n- Cook ground meat if doing tacos Monday\n- Chop veggies for the week\n- Cook rice if using multiple nights\n- Setup slow cooker if needed
LOCATION:Home - Kitchen
CATEGORIES:MEAL-PLANNING
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT

